{"tid":2086271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警終認練射TG 煙攻流浮山","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T08:41:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cab2eccafe62056442adc9bd10a954b9092ba10f","tid":2086271,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200630/QM574KJQGS6RAUMBHD5DGNNKMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200630%2FQM574KJQGS6RAUMBHD5DGNNKMQ%2F&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=4a214372\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200630%2FQM574KJQGS6RAUMBHD5DGNNKMQ%2F&h=802fa90b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200630/QM574KJQGS6RAUMBHD5DGNNKMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警終認練射TG 煙攻流浮山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗流浮山本月1日傳出刺鼻澀眼的不明氣體，令多名市民（圖）不適，包括皮膚灼痛、氣味令人眼淚直流等。警方當日辯稱在屯門青山靶場進行恒常訓練，因訓練中所使用的「訓練煙」意外飄出所致。不過，警方日前就事件回覆立法會時，改口承認當日在訓練中所使用的是「催淚煙」。有議員直斥警方涉嫌講大話，「根本就想淡化事實，明顯呃市民！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鍾國斌：商界憂美辣招制裁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DSgIvSEnXDXnfrXT3p1K_sg-TqQ=/549x308/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GII4PIEQMW4QDMA2DW5K25OMMM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDSgIvSEnXDXnfrXT3p1K_sg-TqQ%3D%2F549x308%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGII4PIEQMW4QDMA2DW5K25OMMM.gif&h=da2bf4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅斥講大話誤導<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅本月1日去信保安事務委員會，要求保安局交代流浮山不明氣體事件。直到上周五警方回覆事件時，改口承認當日有使用催淚煙，「確認警察機動部隊總部於2020年6月1日在青山靶場進行恒常訓練，其<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消防處回覆則指，當日兩次接<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n檢測儀探測後，沒有發現任何可燃或有害氣體。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅直言對警方的回覆感到失望，「警方涉嫌講大話，經常用言語偽<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n樣唔會令同類事件再發生同影響市民」。而截稿前警方未有回覆。"},{"pid":"2ea9283ef5a307c1824dfd8b3c73f9146b150115","tid":2086271,"uid":184581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"成年先認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46911fd4fa3b86aa7887c6eb52755ef7a77698ab","tid":2086271,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea9283ef5a307c1824dfd8b3c73f9146b150115","tid":2086271,"uid":184581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"成年先認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"2020 6月1日 <br />\n5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de898c59c39a1c7e3dd8c54445d4d3ff7f7157da","tid":2086271,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"之前好似仲有另一次㗎啵"},{"pid":"6efc0784af0ef703b1bcbacc056d56e738d70f39","tid":2086271,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"鄉黑韮菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}